data.meta_description:
11 likes, 2 comments - zoescruises on June 13, 2024: "PRINCESS 60th ANNIVERSARY - MEXICO

Celebrate Princess Cruises' 60th Anniversary with a special round-trip cruise from Los Angeles to the heart of Mexico. Join the festivities and discover the vibrant Mexican culture with Zoe's Cruises.

Here are some highlights of this amazing adventure:

Los Angeles, California - Embark on this memorable journey from the bustling city of Los Angeles, a hub of entertainment, culture, and glamour. Before you set sail, explore world-famous attractions like Hollywood, Beverly Hills, or the scenic beaches from Santa Monica to Malibu.

Puerto Vallarta, Jalisco (overnight) - Enjoy an extended stay in Puerto Vallarta, where cobblestone streets meet beautiful beaches. Explore the vibrant Malec칩n boardwalk, the romantic Zona Rom치ntica, or take a day trip to the nearby jungle and hidden coves. The overnight stay allows for sunset views and the chance to experience the local nightlife.

Manzanillo, Colima - Known as the "Sailfish Capital of the World," Manzanillo offers golden beaches and excellent deep-sea fishing. Visit the downtown area for a taste of local life and see the iconic blue sailfish statue.

Mazatl치n, Sinaloa - Dubbed the "Pearl of the Pacific," Mazatl치n boasts a rich historic center and beautiful beaches. Wander the charming Old Town with its 19th-century architecture and bustling market, or relax along the vibrant oceanfront.

Loreto, Baja California Sur - A quieter destination known for its stunning natural beauty and historic missions, Loreto offers a glimpse into Old Mexico. Explore the ancient mission church in the heart of the town or venture out to see the marine life in the Loreto Bay National Marine Park.

Cabo San Lucas, Baja California Sur (overnight) - Another opportunity for an overnight stay, Cabo San Lucas is famous for its dramatic landscapes, including the iconic El Arco. Enjoy water sports, upscale resorts, and vibrant nightlife, or simply relax on the beach.

Los Angeles, California - Return to Los Angeles with a treasure trove of memories from your festive journey along the Mexican Riviera.

#PrincessAnniversary #MexicoCruise #ZoesCruises #FiestaAtSea".
